    <url>/2022/04/15/NexT-config/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="设置fork-me-on-github图标">设置Fork me on github图标</h2>
<ul>
<li>在<code>\themes\next\layout\_layout.swig</code>下找到如下代码块</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&amp;lt;div <span class="keyword">class</span>=&amp;quot;&#123;&#123; container_class &#125;&#125; &#123;% block page_class %&#125;&#123;% endblock %&#125; &amp;quot;&amp;gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &amp;lt;div <span class="keyword">class</span>=&amp;quot;headband&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>添加自己喜欢的样式</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&amp;lt;div <span class="keyword">class</span>=&amp;quot;&#123;&#123; container_class &#125;&#125; &#123;% block page_class %&#125;&#123;% endblock %&#125; &amp;quot;&amp;gt;</span><br><span class="line">   &amp;lt;div <span class="keyword">class</span>=&amp;quot;headband&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;</span><br><span class="line">&amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;https://github.com/zengfanyongcn/zengfanyongcn.github.io&amp;quot; <span class="keyword">class</span>=&amp;quot;github-corner&amp;quot; aria-label=&amp;quot;View source on GitHub&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;svg width=&amp;quot;<span class="number">80</span>&amp;quot; height=&amp;quot;<span class="number">80</span>&amp;quot; viewBox=&amp;quot;<span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">250</span> <span class="number">250</span>&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;fill:<span class="comment">#151513; color:#fff; position: absolute; top: 0; border: 0; right: 0;&amp;quot; aria-hidden=&amp;quot;true&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;path d=&amp;quot;M0,0 L115,115 L130,115 L142,142 L250,250 L250,0 Z&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/path&amp;gt;&amp;lt;path d=&amp;quot;M128.3,109.0 C113.8,99.7 119.0,89.6 119.0,89.6 C122.0,82.7 120.5,78.6 120.5,78.6 C119.2,72.0 123.4,76.3 123.4,76.3 C127.3,80.9 125.5,87.3 125.5,87.3 C122.9,97.6 130.6,101.9 134.4,103.2&amp;quot; fill=&amp;quot;currentColor&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;transform-origin: 130px 106px;&amp;quot; class=&amp;quot;octo-arm&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/path&amp;gt;&amp;lt;path d=&amp;quot;M115.0,115.0 C114.9,115.1 118.7,116.5 119.8,115.4 L133.7,101.6 C136.9,99.2 139.9,98.4 142.2,98.6 C133.8,88.0 127.5,74.4 143.8,58.0 C148.5,53.4 154.0,51.2 159.7,51.0 C160.3,49.4 163.2,43.6 171.4,40.1 C171.4,40.1 176.1,42.5 178.8,56.2 C183.1,58.6 187.2,61.8 190.9,65.4 C194.5,69.0 197.7,73.2 200.1,77.6 C213.8,80.2 216.3,84.9 216.3,84.9 C212.7,93.1 206.9,96.0 205.4,96.6 C205.1,102.4 203.0,107.8 198.3,112.5 C181.9,128.9 168.3,122.5 157.7,114.1 C157.9,116.9 156.7,120.9 152.7,124.9 L141.0,136.5 C139.8,137.7 141.6,141.9 141.8,141.8 Z&amp;quot; fill=&amp;quot;currentColor&amp;quot; class=&amp;quot;octo-body&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/path&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&amp;lt;style&amp;gt;.github-corner:hover .octo-arm&#123;animation:octocat-wave 560ms ease-in-out&#125;@keyframes octocat-wave&#123;0%,100%&#123;transform:rotate(0)&#125;20%,60%&#123;transform:rotate(-25deg)&#125;40%,80%&#123;transform:rotate(10deg)&#125;&#125;@media (max-width:500px)&#123;.github-corner:hover .octo-arm&#123;animation:none&#125;.github-corner .octo-arm&#123;animation:octocat-wave 560ms ease-in-out&#125;&#125;&amp;lt;/style&amp;gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="hexo自定义网站的favicon图标">hexo自定义网站的Favicon图标</h2>
<ul>
<li>制作ico图标32*32，网站： <a href="https://www.logosc.cn/logo/favicon?s=z">https://www.logosc.cn/logo/favicon?s=z</a> 图标名<code>favicon.ico</code></li>
<li>放在<code>themes\next\source\images</code>文件下</li>
<li>修改主题配置文件，路径<code>themes\next\_config.yml</code>，如下所示</li>
</ul>
<p><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">favicon:</span><br><span class="line">  small: /images/favicon-16x16-<span class="built_in">next</span>.png</span><br><span class="line">  medium: /images/favicon.ico</span><br><span class="line">  apple_touch_icon: /images/apple-touch-icon-<span class="built_in">next</span>.png</span><br><span class="line">  safari_pinned_tab: /images/logo.svg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="每篇文章末尾统一添加本文结束标记">每篇文章末尾统一添加“本文结束”标记</h2>
<ul>
<li>在目录<code>themes/next/layout/_macro/</code>下添加<code>passage-end-tag.swig</code> ，内容如下：</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&amp;lt;div&amp;gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> is_index %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &amp;lt;div style=&amp;quot;text-align:center;color: <span class="comment">#ccc;font-size:14px;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;------ 本文结束------&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>打开 <code>themes/next/layout/_macro/post.njk</code> 文件，在<code>&lt;footer class="post-footer"&gt;</code>之前新增内容如下:</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&amp;lt;div&amp;gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> is_index %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% include <span class="string">&#x27;passage-end-tag.swig&#x27;</span> %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"> &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>打开主题配置文件<code>_config.yml</code> ，添加代码如下：</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 文章末尾添加“本文结束”标记</span></span><br><span class="line">passage_end_tag:</span><br><span class="line">enabled: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="在网站底部加上访问量">在网站底部加上访问量</h2>
<p>打开<code>themes\\next\\layout\\\_partials\\footer.njk</code>文件，在<code>&lt;div class="copyright"&gt;</code>之前加上</p>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&amp;lt;script <span class="keyword">async</span> src=&amp;quot;https://dn-lbstatics.qbox.me/busuanzi/<span class="number">2.3</span>/busuanzi.pure.mini.js&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/script&amp;gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&amp;lt;div <span class="keyword">class</span>=&amp;quot;powered-by&amp;quot;&amp;gt;</span><br><span class="line">&amp;lt;i <span class="keyword">class</span>=&amp;quot;fa fa-user-md&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/i&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span <span class="built_in">id</span>=&amp;quot;busuanzi_container_site_uv&amp;quot;&amp;gt;</span><br><span class="line">  本站访客数:&amp;lt;span <span class="built_in">id</span>=&amp;quot;busuanzi_value_site_uv&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;</span><br><span class="line">&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;</span><br><span class="line">&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="添加readme.md文件">添加<code>readme.md</code>文件</h2>
<p>在<code>hexo</code>目录下的<code>source</code>文件夹下添加一个<code>README.md</code>文件，修改站点配置文件，将<code>skip_render</code>参数值设置为</p>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">skip_render: readme.md</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="隐藏网页底部的由hexoampnext.pisces强力驱动">隐藏网页底部的<code>由Hexo&amp;amp;NexT.Pisces强力驱动</code></h2>
<p>打开<code>themes\next\layout\_partials\footer.njk</code>，使用<code>&amp;lt;!-- --&amp;gt;</code>隐藏代码，如下所示</p>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&amp;lt;!--&amp;lt;div <span class="keyword">class</span>=&amp;quot;powered-by&amp;quot;&amp;gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;%- <span class="built_in">set</span> next_site = <span class="string">&#x27;https://theme-next.js.org&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> theme.scheme === <span class="string">&#x27;Gemini&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="string">&#x27;https://theme-next.js.org/&#x27;</span> + theme.scheme | lower + <span class="string">&#x27;/&#x27;</span> %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;&#123;- __(<span class="string">&#x27;footer.powered&#x27;</span>, next_url(<span class="string">&#x27;https://hexo.io&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;Hexo&#x27;</span>) + <span class="string">&#x27; &amp;amp; &#x27;</span> + next_url(next_site, <span class="string">&#x27;NexT.&#x27;</span> + theme.scheme)) &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;</span><br><span class="line">--&amp;gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="实现rss">实现<code>RSS</code></h2>
<ul>
<li>在<code>blog</code>文件夹下安装<code>Hexo</code>插件</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install --save hexo-generator-feed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>在站点配置文件末尾添加：</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Extensions</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Plugins: http://hexo.io/plugins/</span></span><br><span class="line">plugins: hexo-generate-feed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>在主题配置文件下设置<code>rss</code>如下</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rss: /atom.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><span class="math display">\[ y=f(x) \]</span></p>
]]></content>
